{"tid":1258690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息：仁濟及伊利沙伯醫院暫取消警員駐守警崗","createTime":"2019-06-26T08:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T09:10:13.000Z","uid":35221,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"86dc9012022a2a4034ff28623ace6fd854e13cba","tid":1258690,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:35:18.000Z","msg":"消息：仁濟及伊利沙伯醫院暫取消警員駐守警崗<br />\n<br />\n2019-06-26 HKT 16:08<br />\n<br />\n消息透露，仁濟醫院及伊利沙伯醫院今日暫時取消警員駐守警崗，但會在醫院周邊範圍巡邏，有需要時會返回警崗位置。消息人士又表示，不會影響對市民的服務。<br />\n<br />\n另外，醫管局消息人士表示，伊利沙伯醫院中午收到警方通知，今天會取消派員駐守警崗。醫管局已表達關注，希望大家以公眾利益為前提，大家緊守崗位，為市民服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1465135-20190626.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1465135-20190626.htm&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmSLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=cc0d6a4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1465135-20190626.htm&h=da7ca107\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1465135-20190626.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a1c3501621da8f897dd1e2aca20b21768a2a2f6c","tid":1258690,"uid":35221,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:37:20.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母早幾日就係直接喺仁濟拉人"},{"pid":"c06af9d739e88195c28b83c2ec0c533e8b3f910a","tid":1258690,"uid":217844,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:37:27.000Z","msg":"爛仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係經過依幾個星期先知<br />\n原來我地香港警察質素有幾低<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463346baea8b50982e9b7b6a64b8a85da3fd86c7","tid":1258690,"uid":43327,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:38:28.000Z","msg":"支持警方加入不合作運動"},{"pid":"1738d212f164c596cbc05d435eaea55a7ff5b9e9","tid":1258690,"uid":55913